Analyse the RPC mode API and describe its required behaviour as a state machine in plain English, deliberately abstracting away the current implementation's internals so they do not constrain the rewrite. The analysis must cover every externally visible state, every legal transition (including who triggers it and what observable side-effects accompany it), and every command-to-state gate (which commands are accepted or rejected in each state and why). Write the result to a file named `RPC-mode.md` in this objective's directory.
